snippet.title: Dawn Raider gameplay (PC Game, 1990)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Dawn Raider, Dos PC game produced by Softstar Entertainment in 1990 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/dawn-raider/5809/
Blasting aliens in this intense old-school vertically scrolling shooter.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
